reviewText:
The DVDs I did receive were excellent although I was expecting the whole set rather
than just 2 dvds, but for what I paid I was more than pleased.
This DVD highlights Bill Anderson's career with his country music friends celebrating and singing his greatest hits. A must for the country music fan

This is one DVD put out by Country Family Reunion you will not want to miss.  This is probably the best that they have ever put out.  If you like Bill Anderson you will love this dvd.  If I could give this one 10 stars I would.
